headline: DR Horton & Lennar are the Walmart & Costco of homebuilders
summary: Lennar (LEN) stock is under pressure after reporting third quarter results and a disappointing outlook. Smead Capital Management chief investment officer Bill Smead joins Market Catalysts host Julie Hyman to discuss the state of the homebuilder sector (XHB) and how investors should play it. To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Market Catalysts.
